Primljena si!

889
01:01:06,694 --> 01:01:10,775
Pa... pa, u redu.
Ako on tako kae, ja nemam...

890
01:01:12,536 --> 01:01:14,777
Sekretarice-recepcionarko.

891
01:01:14,857 --> 01:01:17,258
Moda bi mogla malo
pospremiti prostorju.

892
01:01:17,338 --> 01:01:19,298
Pospremiti?

893
01:01:19,378 --> 01:01:21,739
Smena re.
ta znai?

894
01:01:21,820 --> 01:01:24,500
Zna, oistiti.
Da izgleda Iepe.

895
01:01:24,580 --> 01:01:28,102
O, da. Ulla moe pospremiti.
Vrlo dobro.

896
01:01:28,181 --> 01:01:30,262
Kad moe doi
sutra ujutro?

897
01:01:30,342 --> 01:01:33,464
Pa, Ulla ustaje svako jutro,
u 5 sati.

898
01:01:33,543 --> 01:01:36,144
Od 5 do 7 Ulla
voli da veba.

899
01:01:36,225 --> 01:01:39,265
Od 7 do 8
Ulla voli da se dugo tuira.

900
01:01:39,346 --> 01:01:43,467
Od 8-9, Ulla voli da jede
obilan vedski doruak.

901
01:01:43,547 --> 01:01:45,467
Mnogo razliitih haringi.

902
01:01:45,548 --> 01:01:49,309
Od 9-11, Ulla voli da vjeba
da pjeva i igra.

903
01:01:49,389 --> 01:01:52,951
I u 11,
Ulla voli da vodi Ijubav.

904
01:01:53,030 --> 01:01:55,511
Kad treba da doem.

905
01:01:55,511 --> 01:01:56,632
U jedanaest.

906
01:01:56,711 --> 01:01:59,513
Dobro.
Ulla e doi u 11.

907
01:01:59,592 --> 01:02:02,674
Ulla e doi u 11.

908
01:02:10,996 --> 01:02:13,958
Bog blagoslovio Ameriku.

909
01:02:15,838 --> 01:02:18,719
Bog blagoslovio vedsku.

910
01:02:18,799 --> 01:02:22,321
Max, fantastina je.

911
01:02:22,401 --> 01:02:25,001
Najlepa devojka koju sam ikada video.

912
01:02:25,082 --> 01:02:26,642
Nikada se ranije nisam ovako oseao.

913
01:02:26,723 --> 01:02:29,803
Kao da je u meni
erupcija vulkana...

914
01:02:29,884 --> 01:02:34,966
...kao da se vrela lava die
i sve vie i vie...

915
01:02:35,085 --> 01:02:37,006
ta je to, Max?

916
01:02:37,126 --> 01:02:39,607
ta je?

917
01:02:40,767 --> 01:02:44,768
Zove se erekcija.
Ili to ili malarija.

918
01:02:45,089 --> 01:02:47,329
Ali, ne brini.
Sad imaju inekcije za sve.

919
01:02:47,410 --> 01:02:49,130
Doi ovamo,
hou da ti pokaem neto.

920
01:02:51,011 --> 01:02:52,851
ta vidi?
Nita.

921
01:02:52,932 --> 01:02:56,292
Tano tako.
Ali, sad kada imamo sigurni neuspeh...

922
01:02:56,372 --> 01:02:59,654
...na posao e biti da taj sef
napunimo sa 2 miliona dolara.

923
01:02:59,734 --> 01:03:03,776
Dva miliona?
Koliko mi ulaemo?

924
01:03:13,379 --> 01:03:17,180
Koliko?
Koliko mi ulaemo?

925
01:03:17,260 --> 01:03:19,020
Bloom...

926
01:03:19,101 --> 01:03:22,502
...dva kardinalna pravila
brodvejskog producenta su,...

927
01:03:22,581 --> 01:03:25,823
...prvo:
nikad ne ulai svoj novac u predstavu....

928
01:03:25,903 --> 01:03:27,143
A drugo?

929
01:03:27,224 --> 01:03:33,065
Nikad ne ulai svoj novac u predstavu!

930
01:03:34,186 --> 01:03:35,707
Razumeo?
Razumeo.

931
01:03:35,786 --> 01:03:37,827
Dobro.
Kako emo skupiti novac?

932
01:03:37,907 --> 01:03:40,828
Kako?
Rei u ti kako.

933
01:03:41,629 --> 01:03:43,109
Od mojih investitora.

934
01:03:43,189 --> 01:03:45,030
Stotine starih damica...

935
01:03:45,109 --> 01:03:50,152
...koje od Maxa Bialystocka trae poslednje
uzbuenje na njihovom putu ka groblju.

936
01:03:50,232 --> 01:03:54,033
Zato e me u narednim danima, Bloom,
veoma retko viati.

937
01:03:54,113 --> 01:03:56,554
A sad,
ja ne elim da vidim tebe.

938
01:03:56,594 --> 01:03:58,475
isti se dok se ja spremam.

939
01:03:58,554 --> 01:04:02,556
Jer, Max Bialystock se sprema
da se lansira...

940
01:04:02,636 --> 01:04:05,317
...u zemlju starih damica.

941
01:04:06,237 --> 01:04:09,198
Dolo je vreme...

942
01:04:09,238 --> 01:04:13,639
...da budem Ijubavnik iz Argentine...

943
01:04:13,720 --> 01:04:18,402
...da zaliem kosu brilijantinom.

944
01:05:49,033 --> 01:05:51,835
Ko je?
Ko je?

945
01:05:51,914 --> 01:05:54,196
Max Bialystock.

946
01:05:57,796 --> 01:06:00,077
Maxy.

947
01:08:07,322 --> 01:08:09,762
Hvala.

948
01:08:19,846 --> 01:08:21,927
Bloom!
Bloom!

949
01:08:21,927 --> 01:08:24,128
ta, Max?
ta?

950
01:08:24,208 --> 01:08:26,928
Uspeo sam.
Uspeo sam, skupio sam 2 miliona.

951
01:08:27,009 --> 01:08:29,809
Sad sve to nam je initi je
da izvedemo najvei neuspeh u istoriji.

952
01:08:29,890 --> 01:08:32,410
To je divno!

953
01:08:42,014 --> 01:08:43,615
Ne moemo da promaimo.

954
01:09:03,862 --> 01:09:06,623
Do 3 sata moram da pustim
jo jednu uplatu pozoritu, inae...

955
01:09:06,703 --> 01:09:08,064
Izvinite,
pogrena kancelarija.

956
01:09:08,143 --> 01:09:10,384
Bialystock.
Bloom.

957
01:09:11,065 --> 01:09:12,905
Max.
Leo.

958
01:09:27,390 --> 01:09:29,951
Ulla?

959
01:09:30,030 --> 01:09:31,471
ta se desilo sa kancelarijom?

960
01:09:31,551 --> 01:09:34,953
Kako ste rekli Ulli,
"pospremi"

961
01:09:36,994 --> 01:09:39,034
Kako si nala vremena
za sve ovo?

962
01:09:39,114 --> 01:09:42,555
Preskoila sam ruak.
Naravno.

963
01:09:42,636 --> 01:09:45,436
Fino.
Preskoila je ruak.

964
01:09:45,517 --> 01:09:47,197
Skoro e tri.
Ta uplata Shubertovima.

965
01:09:47,277 --> 01:09:48,877
Uzei pare iz sefa.

966
01:09:48,958 --> 01:09:51,038
Ti se postaraj
da svi ti ugovori budu potpisani.

967
01:09:51,119 --> 01:09:52,839
Da, Max.

968
01:09:54,119 --> 01:09:56,680
Ofarbala je brojeve.

969
01:10:09,725 --> 01:10:12,086
Zdravo, momci.

970
01:10:13,686 --> 01:10:16,487
Niko ne zna ta sam proao
da doem do vas.

971
01:10:16,567 --> 01:10:18,088
Ulla zna.

972
01:10:18,168 --> 01:10:22,609
Morao si zadovoljiti svaku
staru damicu u Nju Jorku.

973
01:10:24,170 --> 01:10:26,731
Tako je.
Tako je.

974
01:10:27,131 --> 01:10:30,452
Jo uvek imam
ujede kao dokaz.

975
01:10:31,333 --> 01:10:35,254
Posao, posao, posao...

976
01:10:36,254 --> 01:10:41,136
Pa, g. Bloom.

977
01:10:41,216 --> 01:10:43,897
Samo smo.

978
01:10:43,977 --> 01:10:46,858
Da, jesmo,
zar ne?

979
01:10:51,900 --> 01:10:55,661
Zato Bloom bei od Ulle?

980
01:10:56,061 --> 01:10:58,862
Ulla ne svia Bloomu?

981
01:10:58,942 --> 01:11:01,663
Bloom svia Ulli.

982
01:11:01,743 --> 01:11:03,984
Ulla svia Bloomu.

983
01:11:04,064 --> 01:11:07,185
Moda i previe.
Dobro.

984
01:11:07,265 --> 01:11:09,666
Drago mi je.

985
01:11:11,066 --> 01:11:13,107
Zato Bloomu treba
plavo ebence?

986
01:11:13,188 --> 01:11:15,028
Nita bitno.

987
01:11:15,028 --> 01:11:17,029
Samo manji poremeaj.
Imam ga jo od...

988
01:11:17,108 --> 01:11:19,910
...kako sam bio mala beba,
i ja...

989
01:11:19,989 --> 01:11:23,351
Malo si preblizu.

990
01:13:17,351 --> 01:13:19,632
Bloom pomogne Ulli da sie?

991
01:13:19,712 --> 01:13:23,753
U redu.
Bloom pomogne Ulli da sie.

992
01:16:40,703 --> 01:16:43,623
Ponovo!
Arabeska, spremite se...

993
01:16:43,703 --> 01:16:45,624
...pirueta i brz okret.

994
01:16:45,704 --> 01:16:47,865
I guiji korak,
guiji korak...

995
01:16:47,945 --> 01:16:50,225
valc-klog i ponovo!

996
01:17:00,709 --> 01:17:02,230
Halt!

997
01:17:02,310 --> 01:17:05,311
Halt!

998
01:17:05,391 --> 01:17:08,112
Ovo je ludnica!
Ludnica!

999
01:17:10,553 --> 01:17:12,834
Zaveite!

1000
01:17:13,474 --> 01:17:15,155
Moramo da napravimo reda ovde.

1001
01:17:15,234 --> 01:17:17,955
Molim da svi Hitleri-plesai
saekaju sa desne strane bine...

1002
01:17:18,036 --> 01:17:21,916
...a Hitleri-pevai
sa leve strane.

1003
01:17:22,117 --> 01:17:23,877
Idi tamo.

1004
01:17:23,957 --> 01:17:26,959
Carmen, zovi Hitlere-pevae, molim.

1005
01:17:27,039 --> 01:17:29,800
Da, dragi...
Roger.

1006
01:17:37,722 --> 01:17:40,524
"Jacques LaPidus."

1007
01:17:43,925 --> 01:17:46,765
"Jacques LaPidus."

1008
01:17:49,447 --> 01:17:51,808
Jack Lapidus.

1009
01:17:51,887 --> 01:17:54,809
Pa, Jack, ta e
nam otpevati?

1010
01:17:54,929 --> 01:17:59,891
Otpevau
"Lutajui pjeva ja"

1011
01:17:59,930 --> 01:18:02,371
Ako mora.

1012
01:18:11,695 --> 01:18:12,814
Hvala!

1013
01:18:12,895 --> 01:18:15,096
Sledei, molim!

1014
01:18:15,896 --> 01:18:18,336
"Donald Dinsmore."

1015
01:18:18,417 --> 01:18:21,057
Pa, Donald, ako...

1016
01:18:22,258 --> 01:18:23,619
Pa, Donald, ja...

1017
01:18:23,698 --> 01:18:25,859
Zdravo, kako si?
U redu je, donald.

1018
01:18:25,940 --> 01:18:27,180
Zdravo.
Da.

1019
01:18:27,260 --> 01:18:29,501
ta e nam otpevati, prijatelju?

1020
01:18:29,580 --> 01:18:34,863
Otpevau
"Malog drvenog deaka"

1021
01:18:35,943 --> 01:18:37,984
Hvala.

1022
01:18:46,107 --> 01:18:48,347
Sledei.

1023
01:18:49,467 --> 01:18:52,149
"Jason Green."

1024
01:18:53,589 --> 01:18:56,029
Pa, Jason,
ta si radio u poslednje vreme?

1025
01:18:56,110 --> 01:19:00,191
Poslednjih 16 godina sam
imao turneju No No Nie.

1026
01:19:00,272 --> 01:19:02,632
Igrao si Niea?
Ne, ne.

1027
01:19:02,712 --> 01:19:04,393
ta e nam otpevati?

1028
01:19:04,473 --> 01:19:06,674
"Jeste li kad uli
nemaki bend?"

1029
01:19:06,753 --> 01:19:08,915
Ne.
Tako se zove pesma...

1030
01:19:08,994 --> 01:19:11,516
...koju u pevati.

1031
01:19:12,596 --> 01:19:14,556
Muzika, molim.

1032
01:19:17,717 --> 01:19:19,518
Ubrzaj.

1033
01:19:33,443 --> 01:19:36,244
Halt!
Halt!

1034
01:19:36,324 --> 01:19:39,205
Halt!
Ne. ne.

1035
01:19:39,285 --> 01:19:42,086
Ovaj ovek ne moe
da glumi Adolfa Hitlera.

1036
01:19:42,166 --> 01:19:44,887
Firer nije bio mali
musavi mamin sin.

1037
01:19:44,967 --> 01:19:46,527
Firet je bio mukobanjast.

1038
01:19:46,568 --> 01:19:47,968
I tako se ne peva

1039
01:19:48,048 --> 01:19:49,849
"Haben Sie gehrt
das deutsche Band?"

1040
01:19:49,929 --> 01:19:52,530
Ovako se peva " Haben Sie gehrt
das deutsche Band?"

1041
01:19:52,610 --> 01:19:54,971
B- nisko.

1042
01:21:07,196 --> 01:21:09,717
To je na Hitler!

1043
01:21:17,760 --> 01:21:21,361
Spremite karte.
Pripremite karte.

1044
01:21:21,441 --> 01:21:23,922
Ovuda, molim.

1045
01:21:24,002 --> 01:21:26,562
Sedite.

1046
01:21:29,964 --> 01:21:32,405
Dobro vee, gospodine.
Lepo je videti vas.

1047
01:21:32,485 --> 01:21:35,366
Uivajte u predatavi.
Hvala.

1048
01:21:40,768 --> 01:21:42,408
G. Bloom.

1049
01:21:42,488 --> 01:21:46,210
Tako si zgodan.
Hvala.

1050
01:21:46,530 --> 01:21:48,410
Leo!

1051
01:21:50,011 --> 01:21:52,932
Leo, ko ti je rakao
da moe da stavi taj eir?

1052
01:21:53,012 --> 01:21:56,574
Niko, Max. Ali sam mislio, sad kad
sam producent brodvejske predstave...

1053
01:21:56,653 --> 01:21:58,454
Jel' zavesa dignuta?
Ne.

1054
01:21:58,534 --> 01:22:00,255
Je li sputena
Ne.

1055
01:22:00,334 --> 01:22:02,695
Onda jo nisi producent.
Daj mi taj eir.

1056
01:22:02,775 --> 01:22:05,376
G. Bloom! Leo.

1057
01:22:05,457 --> 01:22:08,057
Mana ti se malo ukrivila.

1058
01:22:08,137 --> 01:22:10,458
Ukrivila.
Hvala, Ulla.

1059
01:22:10,538 --> 01:22:12,939
elim ti dobru predstavu.

1060
01:22:22,343 --> 01:22:24,063
Pokuau.

1061
01:22:24,143 --> 01:22:27,424
Ali, mnogo ih ima.

1062
01:22:30,145 --> 01:22:33,146
Mislio sam da smo partneri,
da delimo sve pola-pola.

1063
01:22:33,227 --> 01:22:36,427
Sad sam ja napolju na hladnom
dok se vas dvoje krivite.

1064
01:22:36,508 --> 01:22:38,068
Krivimo?
Nikad, Max.

1065
01:22:38,148 --> 01:22:41,669
Grlimo se i Ijubimo,
da, ali, samo toliko.

1066
01:22:50,233 --> 01:22:54,154
Gunter, pokupie me ovde
odmah nakon zavese.

1067
01:22:57,514 --> 01:22:59,755
Boe, hoemo li im se dopasti?
Hoe li nas mrziti?

1068
01:22:59,836 --> 01:23:00,956
Neizvesnost me ubija.

1069
01:23:01,036 --> 01:23:04,758
Znam.
Oseam se kao pred poroaj.

1070
01:23:07,278 --> 01:23:12,120
Gospodo, Bialystock i Bloom.
Pa, gospodo.

1071
01:23:12,520 --> 01:23:15,561
A ja samo elim svima
da poelim sreu.

1072
01:23:15,641 --> 01:23:18,763
ta? ta si rekao?
Jezik pregrizao.

1073
01:23:18,842 --> 01:23:21,283
ta je bilo?
Samo sam rekao "sreno".

1074
01:23:21,363 --> 01:23:24,444
Ponovo je to rekao.
Zar ti niko nije rekao?

1075
01:23:24,525 --> 01:23:27,526
Poeleti sreu donosi nesreu
na premijerama.

1076
01:24:28,467 --> 01:24:30,228
Slomi nogu?
Da.

1077
01:24:33,868 --> 01:24:35,470
Sreno.

1078
01:24:44,233 --> 01:24:47,514
Pet minuta do dizanja zavese.
Zavesa se die za pet minuta.

1079
01:24:47,713 --> 01:24:49,834
Kasnim.
Moram da trim.

1080
01:24:49,914 --> 01:24:52,435
Slomi nogu!

1081
01:25:07,880 --> 01:25:09,601
Franz, ta se desilo?

1082
01:25:09,681 --> 01:25:12,722
Slomio sam nogu.

1083
01:25:12,803 --> 01:25:16,683
Sad moramo otkazati predstavu
i svima vratiti novac.

1084
01:25:16,764 --> 01:25:18,324
Da vratimo novac?

1085
01:25:18,405 --> 01:25:19,605
Da vratimo novac?

1086
01:25:19,684 --> 01:25:20,965
Vratimo novac?

1087
01:25:21,045 --> 01:25:23,006
Da to nikad vie nisi rekao.
Da vratimo novac?

1088
01:25:23,086 --> 01:25:24,806
Nikad.
Moramo neto drugo da smislimo.

1089
01:25:24,886 --> 01:25:28,288
Ali, Franz igra Hitlera,
Max i nema zamenu.

1090
01:25:28,368 --> 01:25:31,249
U pravu si. ta da radimo?
Mora da postoji neko reenje.

1091
01:25:31,328 --> 01:25:34,170
Kad bi se samo mogao setiti neega.
Nee...

1092
01:25:34,250 --> 01:25:37,131
Stani. Setio sam se. Roger, ti.
Ti moe glumiti Hitlera.

1093
01:25:37,211 --> 01:25:38,732
Zna svaku reenicu.

1094
01:25:38,811 --> 01:25:42,653
Video sam te na probama, uvek
pomera usne zajedno sa glumcima.

1095
01:25:42,773 --> 01:25:45,454
Znam, to je runa navika.
Pokuavam d je se oslobodim.

1096
01:25:45,534 --> 01:25:48,214
Ali, da ja igram Hitlera? Ne!
Nema anse da to uradim veeras.

1097
01:25:48,295 --> 01:25:50,536
Nemam snage.
Nemam hrabrosti.

1098
01:25:50,575 --> 01:25:52,656
Ne mogu to uiniti!
Ne mogu to uiniti!

1099
01:25:52,736 --> 01:25:54,777
To boli!
Roger.

1100
01:25:54,857 --> 01:25:56,737
Sluaj me.

1101
01:25:56,938 --> 01:25:58,178
Moe to uraditi.

1102
01:25:58,258 --> 01:26:00,499
Znam da to moe uraditi,
i znam da to moe uraditi.

1103
01:26:00,579 --> 01:26:03,020
Celog ivota si akao ovu priliku...

1104
01:26:03,100 --> 01:26:05,941
...i neu dopustiti da je propusti.

1105
01:26:06,661 --> 01:26:11,103
Izai e tamo, budalasta,
histerina, vritava kraljica.

1106
01:26:11,183 --> 01:26:14,064
Ali, vraa se,
velika...

1107
01:26:14,184 --> 01:26:18,786
...brodvejska zvezda.

1108
01:26:19,026 --> 01:26:20,746
U redu.
U pravu si.

1109
01:26:20,826 --> 01:26:23,227
Uiniu to!
Tako mi Boga, uiniu to.

1110
01:26:23,307 --> 01:26:26,508
Moram u minkeraj.
Brzo, donesi Franzove Hitlerove brkove.

1111
01:26:26,588 --> 01:26:30,830
I, da. I moj sreni mlade.

1112
01:26:31,470 --> 01:26:33,350
Imam ga.

1113
01:26:37,552 --> 01:26:39,353
Leo, uvertira.

1114
01:26:39,433 --> 01:26:41,633
Idemo.

1115
01:26:54,558 --> 01:26:57,119
Max.
ta?

1116
01:26:57,199 --> 01:26:59,480
To je to!

1117
01:27:00,560 --> 01:27:04,281
Sreno, Leo.
Sreno, Max.

1118
01:34:36,041 --> 01:34:37,801
