Mir u sudnici!

1345
01:51:08,749 --> 01:51:11,750
I prestanite sa tom sambom.

1346
01:51:12,311 --> 01:51:15,592
Ko ste vi?
Ja sam Leopold Bloom...

1347
01:51:15,671 --> 01:51:18,513
...partner Maxa Bialystocka.

1348
01:51:18,593 --> 01:51:20,913
A ko ste vi, draga?

1349
01:51:20,993 --> 01:51:24,515
Zovem se Ulla Inga
Hansen Benson

1350
01:51:24,595 --> 01:51:29,636
...Yonsen Tallen- Hallen
Svaden Svanson Bloom.

1351
01:51:29,717 --> 01:51:31,317
Bloom?

1352
01:51:31,397 --> 01:51:33,998
Vi ste njegova ena?
Da, asni sude.

1353
01:51:34,078 --> 01:51:37,159
Nije hteo da to radi nevenan.

1354
01:51:37,799 --> 01:51:39,480
Kakav mokljan.

1355
01:51:41,160 --> 01:51:43,482
G. Bloom, zato ste,
zaboga, eleli...

1356
01:51:43,561 --> 01:51:45,962
...da se vratite
i da se predate?

1357
01:51:46,042 --> 01:51:49,003
Zato?
Da govorim u njegovu odbranu.

1358
01:51:49,563 --> 01:51:54,285
Svi znamo da je Max Bialystock
laIjivi, prevarantski...

1359
01:51:54,365 --> 01:51:58,967
...dvolini, Ijigavi,
manipulativni, nepoteni...

1360
01:51:59,047 --> 01:52:00,967
Molim te.

1361
01:52:01,048 --> 01:52:02,808
Nemoj mi pomagati.

1362
01:52:04,409 --> 01:52:07,610
asni sude...
asni sude, mogu li da se obratim sudu?

1363
01:52:08,410 --> 01:52:13,852
Zakon je stvoren da bi Ijude
spreio da nanose nepravdu.

1364
01:52:13,932 --> 01:52:17,693
Kome je Max Bialystock
naneo naprevadu?

1365
01:52:17,774 --> 01:52:20,775
Pa ne ovim dragim damama.
Ne.

1366
01:52:20,854 --> 01:52:23,256
A ni meni,
ne...

1367
01:52:23,376 --> 01:52:25,456
Ne meni.

1368
01:52:25,536 --> 01:52:27,777
Ja sam bio niko.

1369
01:52:27,857 --> 01:52:31,138
Niko me nikada ranije
nije zvao Leo.

1370
01:52:31,218 --> 01:52:34,339
Mislim, asni sude,
znam da ovo nije neka velika pravna stvar...

1371
01:52:34,380 --> 01:52:38,821
...ali, ak i u obdanitu su me svi
uvek zvali Bloom.

1372
01:52:38,901 --> 01:52:42,862
Ono to hou da kaem je
da ak i dok sam bio u Rio...

1373
01:52:42,942 --> 01:52:47,824
i imao sve o emu sam
oduvek sanjao...

1374
01:52:50,625 --> 01:52:53,065
...iznenada sam shvatio...

1375
01:52:53,146 --> 01:52:55,507
...da ovaj ovek...

1376
01:52:56,107 --> 01:52:58,147
...ovaj ovek...

1377
01:54:12,093 --> 01:54:14,014
Leo...

1378
01:54:21,417 --> 01:54:24,218
Nikada nisam shvatio.

1379
01:54:25,018 --> 01:54:28,780
Ti si dobar pjeva.
Hvala.

1380
01:54:28,859 --> 01:54:33,061
Ne, stvarno, kao profesionalac.
Pa, pevam za tebe, Max.

1381
01:54:33,181 --> 01:54:36,542
Pevam, zato to sam ti prijatelj.

1382
01:54:37,262 --> 01:54:39,223
Jesi?

1383
01:54:39,784 --> 01:54:42,704
Imao sam mnogo veza...

1384
01:54:42,785 --> 01:54:44,825
...ali, nikada nikoga od njih
nisam mogao da nazivem prijateljem.

1385
01:54:44,905 --> 01:54:46,986
Ali, kada bolje razmislim,...

1386
01:54:47,066 --> 01:54:50,347
...niko me nikada u stvari
nije ni znao.

1387
01:54:50,467 --> 01:54:54,349
Osim njega.

1388
01:56:33,743 --> 01:56:35,624
Gospodo, srce mi se kida...

1389
01:56:35,704 --> 01:56:38,145
...to moram da prekinem
tako divno prijateljstvo.

1390
01:56:38,225 --> 01:56:39,946
Zato, neu.

1391
01:56:40,025 --> 01:56:43,147
Pet godina
u dravnom zatvoru Sing Sing.

1392
01:57:06,995 --> 01:57:09,356
estitam.

1393
01:57:10,516 --> 01:57:14,037
Sad posedujete 45%...

1394
01:57:15,758 --> 01:57:17,959
...zatvorenika Ijubavi.
Sledei!

1395
01:57:18,039 --> 01:57:20,479
Koliko si prodao do sada?
600%.

1396
01:57:20,560 --> 01:57:24,361
Jel' to sve? Nastavi da prodaje.
Nastavi.

1397
01:57:24,561 --> 01:57:28,442
U redu, Prekidaj.
Tiina. Daj mi to.

1398
01:57:28,523 --> 01:57:30,683
Koliko puta treba da vam
kaem, momci?

1399
01:57:30,764 --> 01:57:33,804
Bez tue noevima
na probama.

1400
01:57:35,846 --> 01:57:37,926
Zdravo, ta je s tobom.
nedostatak ritma?

1401
01:57:38,006 --> 01:57:40,447
Vraaj se u red.
Svi u red, odmah!

1402
01:57:40,526 --> 01:57:42,727
Dobro, ivotinje,
idemo svi zajedno!

1403
01:57:42,808 --> 01:57:45,929
Od vrha!
Udari, Franz!

1404
01:57:50,610 --> 01:57:54,452
Tempo, momci.
Pukupite taj tempo!

1405
01:57:54,531 --> 01:57:56,172
Tako je.

1406
01:57:56,253 --> 01:57:59,294
Dobro, samo ubice.

1407
01:57:59,373 --> 01:58:01,014
Hej, ti.

1408
01:58:01,094 --> 01:58:04,575
Upravnik hoe da
ue u ovo stvar.

1409
01:58:06,776 --> 01:58:09,817
Reci upravniku da sad
poseduje 100% Zatvorenika Ijubavi.

1410
01:58:09,897 --> 01:58:12,458
Hvala.
Pevajte, kriminalci.

1411
01:58:12,538 --> 01:58:14,259
Da vas uju i u samicama.

1412
01:58:14,339 --> 01:58:15,699
Idemo, momci.

1413
01:58:15,779 --> 01:58:19,620
Premijera u Leavenworthu
u subotu vee.

1414
01:58:19,701 --> 01:58:23,662
Hej, Bialystock, Bloom, Liebkind,
dobre vesti.

1415
01:58:23,742 --> 01:58:25,183
Ovo je upravo stiglo od guvernera.

1416
01:58:25,262 --> 01:58:27,544
Gospodo, ovim putem ste pomilovani...

1417
01:58:27,664 --> 01:58:30,705
...zbog toga to ste pesmom i plesom
doneli radost i smeh...

1418
01:58:30,784 --> 01:58:34,666
...u srca svakog ubice, siledije i
seksualnog manijaka u Sing Singu.

1419
01:58:34,746 --> 01:58:37,186
Slobodni ste!
Slobodni?

1420
01:58:37,267 --> 01:58:39,947
Sledea stanica,
Zatvorenici Ijubavi u Brodveju!

1421
01:58:40,028 --> 01:58:44,789
Brodvej!
Adolfe, mora rei ostalim pticama.

